item.title: CVE-2018-7902|2024-08-05T06:37:59.561Z -- huawei%20technologies%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- 1288h%20v5%3B%202288h%20v5
item.description: Huawei 1288H V5 and 288H V5 with software of V100R005C00 have a JSON injection vulnerability. An authenticated, remote attacker can launch a JSON injection to modify the password of administrator. Due to insufficient verification of the input, this could be exploited to obtain the management privilege of the system.
